                    <p>&#160;</p>
                    <div class="Important">
                        <h1>Document Feedback</h1>
                        <p style="text-align: left;">If you notice some way that this document can be improved, we're happy to hear your suggestions. Click on the button below to provide us with your feedback. Please remember, though, that not every issue can be addressed through documentation. So, if you have a specific technical question, please open a support ticket.</p>
                        <p style="text-align: left;">&#160;</p>
                        <p style="text-align: left;"><a class="Button" onClick="sendForm()">Send Feedback to BP Logix</a>
                            <!--<input onclick="sendForm()" type="image" src="../Images/Slide4.jpg" value="Send Feedback to BP Logix" id="btnsubmit" name="btnsubmit" /> -->
